      <title>克洛斯兄弟汽车金融案上诉失败，公司股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/close-brothers-slumps-after-losing-motor-finance-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克洛斯兄弟集团有限公司 (Close Brothers Group Plc) 因其对汽车贷款客户的披露义务而败诉，随后其股价暴跌，该银行表示，此举可能导致其业务“承担重大债务”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/close-brothers-slumps-after-losing-motor-finance-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 11:21:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
