      <title>投资者消化令人失望的业绩，欧洲股市持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/european-stocks-fall-as-remy-mercedes-earnings-disappoint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五基本持平，人头马君度集团 (Remy Cointreau SA) 和梅赛德斯-奔驰集团 (Mercedes-Benz Group AG) 等知名公司的业绩表现不佳，打击了投资者的市场情绪，因投资者正在评估即将发生的多重风险事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/european-stocks-fall-as-remy-mercedes-earnings-disappoint</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 07:08:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
